    <item>
      <title>终端命令</title>
      <link>https://example.org/blog/debian-linux/%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AF%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Apr 2025 18:21:11 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://example.org/blog/debian-linux/%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AF%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h3&gt;一、apt&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;一apt&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%e4%b8%80apt&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h4&gt;1、更新软件包列表&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1更新软件包列表&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#1%e6%9b%b4%e6%96%b0%e8%bd%af%e4%bb%b6%e5%8c%85%e5%88%97%e8%a1%a8&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo apt update&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hx-overflow-x-auto hx-mt-6 hx-flex hx-flex-col hx-rounded-lg hx-border hx-py-4 hx-px-4 contrast-more:hx-border-current contrast-more:dark:hx-border-current hx-border-blue-200 hx-bg-blue-100 hx-text-blue-900 dark:hx-border-blue-200/30 dark:hx-bg-blue-900/30 dark:hx-text-blue-200&#34;&gt;
  &lt;p class=&#34;hx-flex hx-items-center hx-font-medium&#34;&gt;&lt;svg height=16px class=&#34;hx-inline-block hx-align-middle hx-mr-2&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; d=&#34;M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;Note&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;div class=&#34;hx-w-full hx-min-w-0 hx-leading-7&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hx-mt-6 hx-leading-7 first:hx-mt-0&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;仅同步本地软件包索引与配置的软件源中的最新信息，但不会实际安装或升级任何软件。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;2、升级软件包&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;2升级软件包&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#2%e5%8d%87%e7%ba%a7%e8%bd%af%e4%bb%b6%e5%8c%85&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo apt upgrade&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;仅升级当前已安装的软件包，不会主动安装新依赖或删除旧包，适合日常维护，避免因依赖变化而导致系统不稳定。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo apt full-upgrade&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;不仅会升级软件包，还会自动处理依赖关系（安装新依赖或删除冲突的旧包），适合大版本升级，解决复杂的依赖调整。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;3、安装指定的软件包&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;3安装指定的软件包&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#3%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85%e6%8c%87%e5%ae%9a%e7%9a%84%e8%bd%af%e4%bb%b6%e5%8c%85&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo apt install &amp;lt;package_name&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo apt install &amp;lt;package_1&amp;gt; &amp;lt;package_2&amp;gt; &amp;lt;package_3&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>系统配置</title>
      <link>https://example.org/blog/debian-linux/%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Apr 2025 22:25:15 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://example.org/blog/debian-linux/%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h3&gt;一、更改软件仓库镜像源&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;一更改软件仓库镜像源&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%e4%b8%80%e6%9b%b4%e6%94%b9%e8%bd%af%e4%bb%b6%e4%bb%93%e5%ba%93%e9%95%9c%e5%83%8f%e6%ba%90&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;以 TUNA 清华源为例：&lt;a href=&#34;https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/help/kali/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Kali 软件仓库使用帮助&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、在终端中执行命令，使用 vim 编辑器编辑 &lt;code&gt;sources.list&lt;/code&gt; 文件&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo vim /etc/apt/sources.list&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、使用 &lt;code&gt;#&lt;/code&gt; 注释 Kali 官方的镜像源并添加清华源&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-text&#34; data-lang=&#34;text&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;# deb http://http.Kali.org/kali kali-rolling main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib non-free-firmware
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/kali kali-rolling main non-free contrib non-free-firmware&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hx-overflow-x-auto hx-mt-6 hx-flex hx-flex-col hx-rounded-lg hx-border hx-py-4 hx-px-4 contrast-more:hx-border-current contrast-more:dark:hx-border-current hx-border-blue-200 hx-bg-blue-100 hx-text-blue-900 dark:hx-border-blue-200/30 dark:hx-bg-blue-900/30 dark:hx-text-blue-200&#34;&gt;
  &lt;p class=&#34;hx-flex hx-items-center hx-font-medium&#34;&gt;&lt;svg height=16px class=&#34;hx-inline-block hx-align-middle hx-mr-2&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; d=&#34;M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;Note&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;div class=&#34;hx-w-full hx-min-w-0 hx-leading-7&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hx-mt-6 hx-leading-7 first:hx-mt-0&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;以下为更换软件仓库镜像源涉及到的一些问题，可选择性观看。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;details class=&#34;last-of-type:hx-mb-0 hx-rounded-lg hx-bg-neutral-50 dark:hx-bg-neutral-800 hx-p-2 hx-mt-4 hx-group&#34; &gt;
  &lt;summary class=&#34;hx-flex hx-items-center hx-cursor-pointer hx-select-none hx-list-none hx-p-1 hx-rounded hx-transition-colors hover:hx-bg-gray-100 dark:hover:hx-bg-neutral-800 before:hx-mr-1 before:hx-inline-block before:hx-transition-transform before:hx-content-[&#39;&#39;] dark:before:hx-invert rtl:before:hx-rotate-180 group-open:before:hx-rotate-90&#34;&gt;
    &lt;strong class=&#34;hx-text-lg&#34;&gt;为什么要换源&lt;/strong&gt;
  &lt;/summary&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;hx-p-2 hx-overflow-hidden&#34;&gt;
    Kali 使用 &lt;code&gt;apt&lt;/code&gt; 命令安装软件包时会在软件仓库的镜像源中查找并下载安装，但默认的 Kali 官方源服务器位于国外，国内用户直接访问可能速度较慢，甚至出现安装失败的情况，因此需要更换国内镜像源（如清华源）加快软件下载和更新速度
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/details&gt;
&lt;details class=&#34;last-of-type:hx-mb-0 hx-rounded-lg hx-bg-neutral-50 dark:hx-bg-neutral-800 hx-p-2 hx-mt-4 hx-group&#34; &gt;
  &lt;summary class=&#34;hx-flex hx-items-center hx-cursor-pointer hx-select-none hx-list-none hx-p-1 hx-rounded hx-transition-colors hover:hx-bg-gray-100 dark:hover:hx-bg-neutral-800 before:hx-mr-1 before:hx-inline-block before:hx-transition-transform before:hx-content-[&#39;&#39;] dark:before:hx-invert rtl:before:hx-rotate-180 group-open:before:hx-rotate-90&#34;&gt;
    &lt;strong class=&#34;hx-text-lg&#34;&gt;为什么配置有 deb 和 deb-src&lt;/strong&gt;
  &lt;/summary&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;hx-p-2 hx-overflow-hidden&#34;&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;deb：指定二进制软件包的下载地址&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;deb-src：指定源代码包的下载地址&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;普通用户如果只是安装软件而无需源码，就可以禁用 deb-src 甚至删除 deb-src 行以节省 &lt;code&gt;apt update&lt;/code&gt; 时间，如果需要阅读某个软件的源代码、重新编译软件或调试程序等就需要启用 deb-src 下载源码&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/details&gt;
&lt;details class=&#34;last-of-type:hx-mb-0 hx-rounded-lg hx-bg-neutral-50 dark:hx-bg-neutral-800 hx-p-2 hx-mt-4 hx-group&#34; &gt;
  &lt;summary class=&#34;hx-flex hx-items-center hx-cursor-pointer hx-select-none hx-list-none hx-p-1 hx-rounded hx-transition-colors hover:hx-bg-gray-100 dark:hover:hx-bg-neutral-800 before:hx-mr-1 before:hx-inline-block before:hx-transition-transform before:hx-content-[&#39;&#39;] dark:before:hx-invert rtl:before:hx-rotate-180 group-open:before:hx-rotate-90&#34;&gt;
    &lt;strong class=&#34;hx-text-lg&#34;&gt;为什么 /etc/apt 有 sources.list 和 sources.list.d&lt;/strong&gt;
  &lt;/summary&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;hx-p-2 hx-overflow-hidden&#34;&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;sources.list：主配置文件，存放系统默认的软件仓库地址（如官方源、第三方源等）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;sources.list.d：附加配置文件目录，用于存放额外的软件源配置文件（通常以 .list 结尾），不同的软件或第三方源可以单独存放一个文件，避免混在 sources.list 里
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Docker 的源可能存放在 /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Google Chrome 的源可能存放在 /etc/apt/sources.list.d/google-chrome.list&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/details&gt;

